metadata.name: Midnight Drive
metadata.description:
Hope. Wonder. Darkness. Despair. 

No matter the moment, there is one person that will always be there. Grab her tight. Hold her close. Take comfort in the way she moves. 

Midnight Drive is a collection of AI art that reminds us of the mechanisms we use to fend off intrusive thoughts and avoid spiraling into the darkest depths of our minds. 

Grab your keys. Become one with the road youâ€™re driving upon.
